# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# ABR GUID — Australian Business Register web service
# Register at: https://abr.business.gov.au/Documentation/WebServiceRegistration
# Accept the Web Services Agreement before use. The GUID is issued immediately
# after registration. There is no sandbox — all calls are against production.
# Never share or commit this GUID. See docs/decisions/ABR/ for obligations.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
ABR_GUID=
